                </div><div class="multicolumn-card__info"><h3>
                    <a href="/web/20230227115514/https://kinderbeauty.com/pages/made-by-kinder-serums">Made by Kinder</a>
                  </h3><div class="rte"><p>Shop science-backed skincare treatments that are kinder to your skin, your wallet, and the animals. Bonus: 5% of proceeds from each Made by Kinder purchase goes directly to animal charities!</p></div><a class="link animate-arrow" href="/web/20230227115514/https://kinderbeauty.com/pages/made-by-kinder-serums">Shop the Serums<span class="icon-wrap">&nbsp;<svg viewbox="0 0 14 10" fill="none" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" role="presentation" class="icon icon-arrow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
