</div><div id="shopify-section-template--16216866914453__165760968648a4c182" class="shopify-section"><div class="images__text__wrapper">
    <div class="page-width">
        <div class="images__text__wrapper__inner">
            
                <section class="imgtext">
                    <div class="image__wrapper">
                        <img loading="lazy" src="//web.archive.org/web/20230227115514im_/https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0118/0631/0459/files/KB_Website_Glow_Getter_D_1000x1000_7378c8a7-2978-4569-b443-4ccbbcece590.jpg?v=1675201248" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <div class="block__text__wrapper">
                        <h2 class="block__heading block__heading1"><p>What's in the February<strong> Beauty Box?</strong></p></h2>
                        <div class="block__description">Even though February is the shortest month of the year, we’ve made sure that this month’s boxes are still teeming with clean beauty products! So, are you ready to fall in love with the Glowgetter and the Busy Bee?</div>
                        <a href="/web/20230227115514/https://kinderbeauty.com/pages/february-2023-box" class="custom__button">See What's Inside</a>
                    </div>
                </section>
            
            
                <section class="imgtext">
                    <div class="block__text__wrapper">
                        <h2 class="block__heading block__heading2"><p>What's in the KND <strong>Cozy Edition?</strong></p></h2>
                        <div class="block__description__items">
                            
                                <div class="item">
                                    
                                    This winter, give your “you time” a glow-up with the Cozy Edition. This curated collection of self-care moments is like a warm blanket on a cold day; it's an invitation to slow down and be unapologetically self-indulgent. Packed with 10 different products valued at more than $240, this stunning collection includes everything you need to not just survive, but thrive through the winter months.
                                </div>
                            
                            
                            
                            
                        </div>
                        <a href="/web/20230227115514/https://kinderbeauty.com/products/knd-box-cozy-edition" class="custom__button">See What's Inside</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="image__wrapper">
                        <img loading="lazy" src="//web.archive.org/web/20230227115514im_/https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0118/0631/0459/files/KB_Website_KND_Cozy_Edition_1000x1000_e4e874e1-e95e-4cf6-902b-29270747ec25.jpg?v=1669077016" alt="">
                    </div>
                </section>
            

        </div>
    </div>
</div>

