<div class="our__team__wrapper">
    <div class="page-width team__wrapper__inner">
        <div class="img__wrapper__team">
            <picture>
                <source srcset="//web.archive.org/web/20230227115514im_/https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0118/0631/0459/files/Group_15466_1.png?v=1657626561" media="(min-width: 992px)">
                <img loading="lazy" src="//web.archive.org/web/20230227115514im_/https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0118/0631/0459/files/Group_15482_1.png?v=1657804111" alt="">
            </picture>
        </div>
        <div class="block__text__wrapper">
            <h2 class="block__heading"><p>Behind <strong>Kinder Beauty</strong></p></h2>
            <div class="block__description"><p>Kinder Beauty was co-founded by Andrew Bernstein, along with actresses and ethical entrepreneurs, Daniella Monet and Evanna Lynch. Andrew, Daniella, and Evy are long-time animal activists and self-care enthusiasts, who share a deep passion for curating the very best ethical beauty products on the market.</p></div>
            <a href="/web/20230227115514/https://kinderbeauty.com/pages/our-story" class="custom__button">Our Story</a>
                    
